metadata.name: Interiors are always BEAUTIFUL
metadata.description:
Narcissism is one of the more misunderstood terms of our time.

Healthy narcissism involves having a strong sense of self-worth, feeling comfortable in one's own skin, and valuing one's own abilities and achievements without the need for constant validation from others.

Healthy narcissism is characterized by a balanced sense of self-awareness, empathy, and a willingness to consider the perspectives and needs of others.
